snippet.title: Metal Crash - Hard Hatters stage
snippet.description: Btw no, this isn't a "Crash N Tense replacement", N Tense is what replaced this originally. I just went back cos this is a muuuch easier and lighter project to work on and it felt like fun, required sooo much less time than doing stuff for N Tense does.
